description: MST successfully organized a delagation of 17 Taiwanese delegates to participate in the 2023 Harvard WorldMUN conference held in Paris.
Re_Model UN Conference, or Re_MUN was an invitational, experimental pop_up conference held on Aug. 6th, 2022, Re_MUN was also one of the first public events hosted by MST.
